title: Who Am I (and my composers)? - Ep 11
itunes:title: Who Am I (and my composers)? - Ep 11
description:
Vitaliy has long considered himself more American than Russian, so why does he feel that it's the Russian composers (like Rachmaninoff and Tchaikovsky) that speak to his soul? Vitaliy explores this question - and Rachmaninoff's Piano Concerto Number 4 in this episode.

You can read this article online at: https://contrarianedge.com/who-am-i-and-my-composers/

Listen to Rachmaninoff's Piano Concerto Number 4 at: https://myfavoriteclassical.com/who-am-i-and-my-composers/
